 <span data-ttu-id="7dfe6-104">与关联的<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A>值由属性返回。 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7dfe6-104">The <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> value associated with a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> is returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
